omment after new mixed doubles invite  Another said: \\\"Petition for Andy Murray to keep playing doubles please.\\\"\", \"from\": 4850, \"to\": 5040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4858, \"end\": 4871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emma Raducanu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Raducanu\"}, {\"begin\": 4897, \"end\": 4908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Judy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 4996, \"end\": 5007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.433354492645805e-53, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And a fifth wrote: Dear @andy_murray You have shown how awesome you are at doubles too!\", \"from\": 5042, \"to\": 5129, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please please reconsider retiring and just play dubs.\\\"\", \"from\": 5130, \"to\": 5184, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately, however, it's unlikely that Murray will change his mind.\", \"from\": 5186, \"to\": 5257, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5229, \"end\": 5235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.920414954601866e-31, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Injuries have taken a toll on the veteran over the years, with the 37-year-old often forced to play through the pain.\", \"from\": 5259, \"to\": 5376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE:'Disqualify them' - Olympic officials told to boot Rafael Nadal and Carlos Alcaraz out of doubles draw  Winning an Olympic gold would be a brilliant way for him to bow out, however.\", \"from\": 5378, \"to\": 5569, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5439, \"end\": 5451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 5456, \"end\": 5470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some feel it's written in the stars that Murray will add to his medal haul, having previously won gold at Olympics in 2012 and 2016.\", \"from\": 5571, \"to\": 5703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5612, \"end\": 5618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.920414954601866e-31, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that's not something Murray believes, with the former world No 1 keen to stay focused.\", \"from\": 5705, \"to\": 5795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5730, \"end\": 5736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.920414954601866e-31, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We were very lucky in the first match and today we were not,\\\" he admitted.\", \"from\": 5797, \"to\": 5872, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"LATEST SPORTS NEWS:  Andy Murray has impressed playing alongside Dan Evans at the Olympics  PA  \\\"The margins are so fine, we need to perform at a really high level in a couple of days' time to go through.\", \"from\": 5874, \"to\": 6078, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5895, \"end\": 5906, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.433354492645805e-53, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 5939, \"end\": 5948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Die_Warzau\", \"score\": 0.9670267245561914, \"rank\": 0.034097584480756324, \"text\": \"Dan Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Die_Warzau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Die_Warzau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And you build confidence by winning matches like that and I think your opponents see that, that you are coming back when you are behind and that builds belief.\", \"from\": 6080, \"to\": 6240, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But you can not have that mentality of 'Oh this is just going to happen now.'\", \"from\": 6242, \"to\": 6320, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We need to be switched on for the next one and let us see what happens in a couple of days.\\\"\", \"from\": 6321, \"to\": 6413, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray cried after his win with Evans.\", \"from\": 6415, \"to\": 6453, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6415, \"end\": 6421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.920414954601866e-31, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 6447, \"end\": 6452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.999998882232091, \"rank\": 1.1177691911280069e-06, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Andy Murray is hoping to win a third gold medal of his career at the Olympics this summer  PA  Explaining his tears, he added: \\\"Obviously it's unbelievably emotional.\", \"from\": 6455, \"to\": 6621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6455, \"end\": 6466, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.433354492645805e-53, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You are obviously unbelievably happy and then, I do not know why it happens, it's like happy tears.\", \"from\": 6623, \"to\": 6723, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was really emotional at the end of the match.\", \"from\": 6724, \"to\": 6771, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Obviously extremely happy, excited that we managed to get through and another amazing finish so it takes a lot out of you that sort of stuff.\", \"from\": 6773, \"to\": 6915, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am glad we get a day off tomorrow.\\\"\", \"from\": 6917, \"to\": 6955, \"entities\": []}]}"